title: 119: The Trader Joe's Fall Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Trader Joe's Fall Haul Episode
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying fall finds from TJ’s -- maple coffee, pumpkin waffles, cornbread biscotti, pumpkin spice batons, pumpkin empanadas, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, Lisa declares one of the items the best frozen meal she’s ever had!!! So go ahead and jump right in. And when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: This week, Lisa and the gang try fall food finds from Trader Joe's!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
